profile:
We have been installing wood vinyl wrought iron and chain-link Fences is southwestern Ontario for 10 years. in 2021 we became the authorized dealer for a local vinyl manufacture for the Lambton and Chatham-Kent County, and now we only install vinyl fences.  We have 7 colours, offer a  lifetime warranty on the vinyl even if you install it yourself. 
Vinyl FENCE and DECKING Supplier for DIY, or we can Supply and install  Free estimates.
